{"desi_lesson":{"title":"Asking Simple Questions","target_language":"Kannada","theme":"Asking Simple Questions","vocabulary":[{"english":"hello","target_language_script":"ನಮಸ್ತೆ","transliteration":"namaste","pronunciation":"nuh-muh-stay"},{"english":"how are you?","target_language_script":"ನೀವು ಹೇಗಿದ್ದೀರಿ?","transliteration":"nīvu hēgiddiri?","pronunciation":"nee-vu hay-gid-dee-ree?"},{"english":"I am fine","target_language_script":"ನಾನು ಚೆನ್ನಾಗಿದ್ದೇನೆ","transliteration":"nānu chenāgiddēne","pronunciation":"nah-noo che-nah-gid-day-nay"},{"english":"thank you","target_language_script":"ಧನ್ಯವಾದಗಳು","transliteration":"dhanyavādagalu","pronunciation":"dhan-ya-vah-dah-ga-loo"},{"english":"what is your name?","target_language_script":"ನಿಮ್ಮ ಹೆಸರೇನು?","transliteration":"nimma hesarenu?","pronunciation":"nim-ma hey-sa-ray-noo?"},{"english":"my name is...","target_language_script":"ನನ್ನ ಹೆಸರು...","transliteration":"nanna hesaru...","pronunciation":"nan-na hey-sa-roo..."},{"english":"yes","target_language_script":"ಹೌದು","transliteration":"houdu","pronunciation":"how-doo"},{"english":"no","target_language_script":"ಇಲ್ಲ","transliteration":"illa","pronunciation":"il-la"},{"english":"please","target_language_script":"ದಯವಿಟ್ಟು","transliteration":"dayavittu","pronunciation":"day-a-vit-too"},{"english":"excuse me","target_language_script":"ಕ್ಷಮಿಸಿ","transliteration":"kṣamisi","pronunciation":"ksha-mi-see"}],"example_sentences":[{"english":"Hello, how are you?","target_language_script":"ನಮಸ್ತೆ, ನೀವು ಹೇಗಿದ್ದೀರಿ?","transliteration":"namaste, nīvu hēgiddiri?","pronunciation":"nuh-muh-stay, nee-vu hay-gid-dee-ree?"},{"english":"I am fine, thank you.","target_language_script":"ನಾನು ಚೆನ್ನಾಗಿದ್ದೇನೆ, ಧನ್ಯವಾದಗಳು.","transliteration":"nānu chenāgiddēne, dhanyavādagalu.","pronunciation":"nah-noo che-nah-gid-day-nay, dhan-ya-vah-dah-ga-loo."},{"english":"What is your name?","target_language_script":"ನಿಮ್ಮ ಹೆಸರೇನು?","transliteration":"nimma hesarenu?","pronunciation":"nim-ma hey-sa-ray-noo?"},{"english":"My name is John.","target_language_script":"ನನ್ನ ಹೆಸರು ಜಾನ್.","transliteration":"nanna hesaru Jān.","pronunciation":"nan-na hey-sa-roo Jah-n."},{"english":"Please excuse me.","target_language_script":"ಕ್ಷಮಿಸಿ ದಯವಿಟ್ಟು.","transliteration":"kṣamisi dayavittu.","pronunciation":"ksha-mi-see day-a-vit-too."}],"short_story":{"title":"Meeting a New Person","dialogue":[{"speaker":"Person A","target_language_script":"ನಮಸ್ತೆ!","transliteration":"Namaste!","english":"Hello!"},{"speaker":"Person B","target_language_script":"ನಮಸ್ತೆ! ನೀವು ಹೇಗಿದ್ದೀರಿ?","transliteration":"Namaste! Nīvu hēgiddiri?","english":"Hello! How are you?"},{"speaker":"Person A","target_language_script":"ನಾನು ಚೆನ್ನಾಗಿದ್ದೇನೆ, ಧನ್ಯವಾದಗಳು. ನಿಮ್ಮ ಹೆಸರೇನು?","transliteration":"Nānu chenāgiddēne, dhanyavādagalu. Nimma hesarenu?","english":"I am fine, thank you. What is your name?"},{"speaker":"Person B","target_language_script":"ನನ್ನ ಹೆಸರು ರಾಜು. ನಿಮ್ಮದು?","transliteration":"Nanna hesaru Rāju. Nimmadu?","english":"My name is Raju. Yours?"}]},"quiz":[{"question":"How do you say 'how are you?' in Kannada?","options":["nīvu hēgiddiri?","namaste","dhanyavādagalu"],"answer":"nīvu hēgiddiri?"},{"question":"How do you say 'thank you' in Kannada?","options":["namaste","dhanyavādagalu","illa"],"answer":"dhanyavādagalu"},{"question":"What is the Kannada word for 'yes'?","options":["houdu","illa","namaste"],"answer":"houdu"},{"question":"How do you say 'my name is...' in Kannada?","options":["nimma hesarenu?","nanna hesaru...","namaste"],"answer":"nanna hesaru..."}]}}